{
  "texts": [
    "To analyze the Ramachandran plot of different simulations, the free energy value was estimated using the potential of mean force (PMF).",
    "ϕ and ψ were set as two reaction coordinates (x, y).",
    "All three ϕ and ψ dihedrals in Ac-Ala3-NHMe were calculated and plotted.",
    "The relative free energy value was calculated and referred to with the minimum value.",
    "To generate the landscape, 40 bins were used in both the x and y directions."
  ]
}